{"tid":1180043,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"被同事誤會我叫雞，有咩方法呈清，還自己清白？","createTime":"2019-05-31T14:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T17:07:14.000Z","uid":73381,"like":15,"dislike":142,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"379e78eef768bb1fea2ed5517c469b5850998736","tid":1180043,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:02:11.000Z","msg":"前日放工在太子西記側面樓下睇手機等小巴，原來嗰日有個男同事經過還襯我唔知用手機照了我相，到尋日他就同其他同事話見到我係西記側面摟下徘徊，啲同事轉轉下講到我上左去叫雞之後落樓等小巴，連暗戀的女同事也信以為真，我都是之後才知這餐廳側面樓梯上面是一樓一，好冤枉呀我都無叫過雞，我呈清又無人信當我狡辯，最慘想追暗戀女同事也無望，我可你點？"},{"pid":"2e2f1c008586baed1b8fa745232f05ff3b93be08","tid":1180043,"uid":176802,"like":437,"dislike":5,"score":432,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:04:13.000Z","msg":"真係上去叫一次雞<br />\n咁咪唔係誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d761ebf0b457e5c81846c90aad2c94d22a83f348","tid":1180043,"uid":167032,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"叫鴨"},{"pid":"3cff964b5473ad3cd2b1453772b5f2a8345ffecd","tid":1180043,"uid":73381,"like":3,"dislike":98,"score":-95,"quote":{"pid":"2e2f1c008586baed1b8fa745232f05ff3b93be08","tid":1180043,"uid":176802,"like":437,"dislike":5,"score":432,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:04:13.000Z","msg":"真係上去叫一次雞<br />\n咁咪唔係誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:06:11.000Z","msg":"我只吃炸雞，不叫真雞<img src=\"https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default/smile_45.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.discuss.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_45.gif&h=4d16c710&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db0d99fdd18f8bb39850bc6ae6789be7dfc0b9b4","tid":1180043,"uid":73381,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"d761ebf0b457e5c81846c90aad2c94d22a83f348","tid":1180043,"uid":167032,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"叫鴨"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:06:57.000Z","msg":"我